thread_name: RE: app not installing from store to phone.
subject: RE: app not installing from store to phone.
content:
The app vesion is good. Ask him to send another snapshot of message he is getting and create a service now ticket for him.
Or he can bring the cell in to the transit store.
Ask him if he is using data or wifi?
Thank you,
Carol Garcia
Customer Service
